fieldInstances.__value:
playaComp = {
    update do
       this.pos.x = this.pos.x + IMC.movementTD().x * 350 * k.dt()
        this.pos.y = this.pos.y + IMC.movementTD().y * 350 * k.dt()
    end
}

local playa = k.add([
 k.sprite("SpriteSheet3"),
   k.scale(levelSize),
   k.pos(X,Y),
 playaComp,
    k.area(),
    kReset(currentScene, deathScore),
    matterCircle(engine, {}, 8 * levelSize, true),
    k.anchor("center"),
   kCamera(true, null, 2, null),
    "Player"
])


k.onCollideUpdate("Player", "Solid", with a, b, col do
   a.pos.y = a.pos.y + col.displacement.y
   a.pos.x = a.pos.x + col.displacement.x
   IMC.rumble(100)
end)
